            "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Happy business team of young multi-ethnic office employees celebrating victory and big profit.\" data-id=\"1367482914\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367482914/image_1367482914.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">dikushin</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It's been a scary few weeks for investors.</p> <p>Stocks are now in a correction, falling from their intraday highs on Tuesday, March 11.</p> <p><strong>Always And Forever A Market Of Stocks, Not A Stock Market</strong></p> <p>Individual stocks?</p> <p>Also, 38% of the S&amp;P 500</p>",
